iswitch-menu is an Emacs extension that aims to make the console menu
interface for emacs much efficient and easy to use, by using iswitchb technology to do the display and navigation.

It's a work in progress, and you can get it at:

http://github.com/joodie/iswitch-menu/tree/master

Motivation and some screen shots:

http://joost.zeekat.nl/2008/09/14/better-consolekeyboard-menus-for-emacs/

See also: MenuAccessFromKeyboard

